- You have to believe me.

651
01:05:00,840 --> 01:05:03,650
Why? Don't we, like,
make our own destiny and stuff?

652
01:05:11,520 --> 01:05:12,646
What?

653
01:05:20,000 --> 01:05:21,331
Who are you, kid?

